description: Lists the created artifacts attached to a given migration task in an update stream. This API has the following traits:

parameters.name: MigrationTaskName
parameters.description: Unique identifier that references the migration task. Do not store personal data in this field.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If there are more created artifacts than the max result, return the next token to be passed to the next call as a bookmark of where to start from.

nested_items.name: CreatedArtifactList
nested_items.description: List of created artifacts up to the maximum number of results specified in the request.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: An ARN that uniquely identifies the result of a migration task.

nested_items.name: Description
nested_items.description: A description that can be free-form text to record additional detail about the artifact for clarity or for later reference.
